				<div class="keyofferings__offerings">
					
					<div class="keyofferings__offerings__item clearfix" id="keyofferings-item-engineering">
						<p>Our engineering offerings include prototyping, designing building CAD models, choosing building specifying  materials, prototyping, testing in the field, technical drawings, and working liasing with manufacturing vendors.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="keyofferings__offerings__item hide clearfix" id="keyofferings-item-ideation">
						<p>Our ideation offerings include brainstorming, idea mapping, concept generation, review, and synthesis, as well as the refined visualization outputs required for advanced iterations.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="keyofferings__offerings__item hide clearfix" id="keyofferings-item-innovation">
						<p>Some problems require more than a revolutionary approach. We offer breakaway strategic thinking to develop new tools that create solutions for stubborn, deep-set problems. Here’s how we’re helping Indonesia’s poor.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="keyofferings__offerings__item hide clearfix" id="keyofferings-item-education">
						<p>We evaluate and identify problems. Collect or create solutions that address those problems. And develop curriculae that clearly convey these learnings with actionable steps. In the example below, we assessed the value local residents placed on electricity.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="keyofferings__offerings__item hide clearfix" id="keyofferings-item-insights">
						<p>We do our best to clear out all the information we’ve stored and simply observe a new place. We take in everything we can, and ask a lot of questions.  And then we interpret what we have observed to find the root of the need. In the example below, we assessed the value local residents placed on electricity.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="keyofferings__offerings__item hide clearfix" id="keyofferings-item-systems_thinking">
						<p>We view our work as one piece in an overall system. Part of our job is understanding how things - mechanically, ecologically, and culturally - influence one another within a whole, so that we are able to design a sustainable solution. In the instance below, we used our learnings to manage local solar vendor selection for installation and maintenance strategy.</p>
					</div>
					
